            <title>[KAFKA-3095] No documentation on format of sasl.kerberos.principal.to.local.rules</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3095</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The documentation talked about the config sasl.kerberos.principal.to.local.rules and the format of the default but it doesn&apos;t say what format the rules should be specified in.  A description and perhaps an example would be very useful here.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
